data.title: David Barger's Profile and Production Credits
data.meta_description: Check out all of David Barger's production credits. Staff Me Up is the #1 site for industry networking and up-to-date credit information.
data.text: Maybe I have always been mesmerized by shiny toys. Maybe I never wanted to work in a job where I had to wear a tie. Maybe I found that I was good at telling a story with images. It is probably all of those things that led me to a career in television.
